## 车载应用性能监控

### 关键指标

| 指标 | 说明 | 目标值 |
|------|------|--------|
| 启动时间 | 冷启动耗时 | < 1s |
| FPS | 帧率 | ≥ 60fps |
| 内存 | 内存占用 | < 100MB |
| CPU | CPU 使用率 | < 30% |
| 卡顿 | 掉帧次数 | < 5次/分钟 |

### 监控实现

**1. 帧率监控**
```java
public class FpsMonitor implements Choreographer.FrameCallback {
    private long mLastFrameTime;
    private int mFrameCount;

    @Override
    public void doFrame(long frameTimeNanos) {
        mFrameCount++;
        long elapsed = frameTimeNanos - mLastFrameTime;

        if (elapsed >= 1000000000L) { // 1秒
            float fps = mFrameCount * 1000000000f / elapsed;
            Log.d("FPS", String.valueOf(fps));
            mFrameCount = 0;
            mLastFrameTime = frameTimeNanos;
        }

        Choreographer.getInstance().postFrameCallback(this);
    }
}
```

**2. 方法耗时监控**
```java
// AOP 方式
@Around("execution(* com.example..*(..))")
public Object logMethodTime(ProceedingJoinPoint joinPoint) throws Throwable {
    long start = System.currentTimeMillis();
    Object result = joinPoint.proceed();
    long cost = System.currentTimeMillis() - start;

    if (cost > 100) {
        Log.w("Perf", joinPoint.getSignature() + " cost " + cost + "ms");
    }
    return result;
}
```

**3. 内存监控**
```java
// 定期检查内存
void checkMemory() {
    ActivityManager.MemoryInfo info = new ActivityManager.MemoryInfo();
    ((ActivityManager) getSystemService(ACTIVITY_SERVICE)).getMemoryInfo(info);

    if (info.lowMemory) {
        // 低内存警告
        onLowMemory();
    }
}
```

**4. ANR 监控**
```java
// 监控主线程卡顿
public class ANRMonitor extends Thread {
    @Override
    public void run() {
        while (true) {
            if (isMainThreadBlocked()) {
                reportANR();
            }
            sleep(5000);
        }
    }
}
```

