## 异常崩溃处理

### 异常捕获

**1. 全局异常捕获**
```java
public class CrashHandler implements Thread.UncaughtExceptionHandler {
    private Thread.UncaughtExceptionHandler mDefaultHandler;

    public void init(Context context) {
        mDefaultHandler = Thread.getDefaultUncaughtExceptionHandler();
        Thread.setDefaultUncaughtExceptionHandler(this);
    }

    @Override
    public void uncaughtException(Thread thread, Throwable ex) {
        // 保存崩溃信息
        saveCrashInfo(ex);

        // 上传崩溃日志
        uploadCrashLog();

        // 调用默认处理器
        mDefaultHandler.uncaughtException(thread, ex);
    }
}
```

**2. 崩溃信息收集**
```java
private String getCrashInfo(Throwable ex) {
    StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();

    // 设备信息
    sb.append("Device: ").append(Build.MODEL).append("\n");
    sb.append("Android: ").append(Build.VERSION.RELEASE).append("\n");

    // 应用版本
    sb.append("Version: ").append(getAppVersion()).append("\n");

    // 崩溃堆栈
    StringWriter sw = new StringWriter();
    ex.printStackTrace(new PrintWriter(sw));
    sb.append(sw.toString());

    return sb.toString();
}
```

**3. 日志上传**
```java
public void uploadCrashLog(String log) {
    // 使用 OkHttp 上传
    OkHttpClient client = new OkHttpClient();
    RequestBody body = RequestBody.create(log, MediaType.parse("text/plain"));
    Request request = new Request.Builder()
        .url("https://api.example.com/crash")
        .post(body)
        .build();

    client.newCall(request).enqueue(new Callback() {
        @Override
        public void onResponse(Call call, Response response) {
            // 上传成功，删除本地日志
            deleteLocalCrashLog();
        }
    });
}
```

